import { AppBar, Box, Link, List, ListItemText, Toolbar, Typography } from "@mui/material"
import FoodBankIcon from '@mui/icons-material/FoodBank';

function Navbar() {
    return (
        <>
            <Box>
                <AppBar>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <Typography>
                            <FoodBankIcon />
                            Al-Baik
                        </Typography>
                        <Box>
                            <List sx={{bgcolor:"black"}}>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link>Home</Link>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link>Menu</Link>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link>About</Link>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link>Contact</Link>
                                </ListItemText>



                            </List>
                        </Box>
                    </Toolbar>
                </AppBar>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
